### Create a new user
POST http://localhost:5000/users
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: supersecretkey

{
  "username": "alice",
  "userAge": "24"
}

### Create another user
POST http://localhost:5000/users
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: supersecretkey

{
  "username": "bob",
  "userAge": "30"
}

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:5000/users
X-Api-Key: supersecretkey

### Get a single user
GET http://localhost:5000/users/alice
X-Api-Key: supersecretkey
### Update a user
PUT http://localhost:5000/users/alice
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: supersecretkey

{
  "username": "alice",
  "userAge": "26"
}

### Delete a user
DELETE http://localhost:5000/users/bob
X-Api-Key: supersecretkey

### Verify deletion
GET http://localhost:5000/users
X-Api-Key: supersecretkey
